        </p>
        <div class="aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <iframe
            src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/730167942?h=0&title=0&byline=0&portrait=0"
            class="w-full h-full"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem/Solution -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
          The design gap is holding you back
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-6">
          If you've ever worked with a designer but you're never happy with the results, there's a design gap. You know what looks good, but you can't articulate why—or create it yourself.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-6">
          This course teaches you the <strong class="text-white">80/20 of design</strong>—the most essential concepts without overwhelming complexity. You'll learn to make sound visual choices without needing to become a professional designer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Line Divider -->
  <div class="flex justify-center py-16">
    <img src="/images/site/line-divider.svg" alt="" class="h-48 md:h-64" />
  </div>

  <!-- Who Is This Course For -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-brand-coral text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-8">Who Is This Course For?</p>

        <!-- Three Cards -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-purple rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3">For coaches & creators</h3>
            <p class="text-white/80">Learn the tools and skills to create stand out graphics for your business, social channels, and websites.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-purple rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3">For aspiring designers</h3>
            <p class="text-white/80">Level up your career by learning the fundamentals of Figma, and making better design decisions in your design projects.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-purple rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3">For PMs, marketers, and developers</h3>
            <p class="text-white/80">Learn the fundamentals of design so you can better communicate and support the designers around you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Video Section -->
        <h2 class="font-display-black-italic text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6">
          Over-the-shoulder videos and walkthroughs for non-designers
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/70 mb-6">
          This course is built for non-designers who care about design, but feel intimidated, scared, or don't have confidence in making design decisions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/70 mb-6">
          It's for the ultimate beginner who wants to feel comfortable using tools like Figma, which allows you to create anything you want.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/70 mb-8">
          You might also be an engineer, PM, or marketing director who wants to better communicate your design needs, but lack the visual communication skills to feel comfortable expressing ideas.
        </p>

        <!-- Figma Walkthrough Video -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <video
            src="/images/products/cdk-figma-walkthrough.mp4"
            autoplay
            loop
            muted
            playsinline
            class="w-full"
          ></video>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Line Divider -->
  <div class="flex justify-center py-16">
    <img src="/images/site/line-divider.svg" alt="" class="h-48 md:h-64" />
